ygData.subject: Re: Qyenos Merchant that sells tiny daggers?
ygData.msgSnippet: I have not yet found anyone in Qeynos who sells tiny daggers. However, Erudin is a short boat ride away, and there they have them for sale in the Enchanters
ygData.messageBody:
I have not yet found anyone in Qeynos who sells tiny daggers. However,
Erudin is a short boat ride away, and there they have them for sale in
the Enchanters Guild.

-----Original Message-----
From: clark@... [mailto:clark@...]
Sent: Thursday, April 29, 1999 11:33 AM
To: eqenchanters@onelist.com
Subject: [eqenchanters] Qyenos Merchant that
sells tiny daggers?

From: clark@...

I have traveled for many days and nights, and fought off
countless perils to reach the Human city of Qyenos. It it very different
than my home city of Ak'anon but I find myself drawn to explore and
learn. Since I have decided to stay in Qyenos for a while I will need an
animation to protect myself from the smelly gnolls. Can any fellow
enchanters tell me the location of the merchant in Qyenos that will sell
me tiny daggers?

Thanks Kindly

Agergon (Tunare)
